     pipeline_name   : str  — parent pipeline identifier
     flowgroup_name  : str  — flowgroup identifier
     actions         : list[dict] — post-expansion concrete action records;
                        each dict has exactly these 8 keys:
                          action_name      : str
                          source_system_id : str
                          schema_name      : str
                          table_name       : str
                          load_group       : str
                          jdbc_table       : str   (B2 Anomaly A regression)
                          watermark_column : str   (B2 Anomaly A regression)
                          landing_path     : str   (B2 Anomaly A regression)
   ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   Control flow (B2 R1, R1a, R2, R9):
     1. UTC session timezone (FR-L-07)
     2. Auto-DDL: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS b2_manifests (R9)
     3. derive_run_id (R1a) — batch_id once at task entry
